Package containing nodes that take care of reading values from variables.

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ReadConstantNode
    Node representing reading constants.
    ReadDereferenceNode
    This node reads dereferenced value of a pointer.
    ReadFromArrayNode
    This nodes read value from an array at specified index.
    ReadFromRecordNode
    This node reads value from an record with specified identifier.
    ReadGlobalVariableNode
    This node reads value of specified global variable (by its frame slot).
    ReadLocalVariableNode

    ReadReferenceVariableNode
    This node reads value from a variable passed by reference.

Package cz.cuni.mff.d3s.trupple.language.nodes.variables.read Description

Package containing nodes that take care of reading values from variables. This reading differs based on the type of the variable. We have different read nodes for primitive variables, records, pointers, etc.
